<section class="problem-section">
<div class="container">
	<div class="section-label">// the problem</div>
	<div class="problem-grid">
		<div class="problem-col before">
			<h3><span class="icon">×</span> Without skill-tools</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Skills are undocumented, scattered across repos</li>
				<li>No way to validate against a spec</li>
				<li>Agent picks wrong skill, wastes tokens</li>
				<li>Hardcoded secrets leak into prompts</li>
				<li>Manual OpenAPI → skill conversion</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="problem-col after">
			<h3><span class="icon">→</span> With skill-tools</h3>
			<ul>
				<li>Portable SKILL.md format, one file per skill</li>
				<li>Validate, lint, score in CI — like ESLint for skills</li>
				<li>BM25 routes queries to the right skill instantly</li>
				<li>8 lint rules catch secrets and hardcoded paths</li>
				<li>Auto-generate from OpenAPI 3.x specs</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
</section>

<style>
	.problem-section { padding: 0; }

	.problem-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.problem-col h3 {
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.icon { font-style: normal; font-size: 0.9rem; }

	.before h3 { color: var(--muted); }
	.after h3 { color: var(--blue); }

	.problem-col ul {
		list-style: none;
		font-family: var(--font-body);
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		color: var(--muted);
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	.problem-col ul li::before {
		content: '—';
		margin-right: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--dim);
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.problem-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
	}
</style>
